Notes:
 Running candy with multi instances

   1) Using OpenRC
    Prepare /etc/candy.d/${foo}.cfg first
    # ln -s /etc/init.d/{candy,${foo}}
    # rc-service ${foo} start
    # rc-update add ${foo} default

   2) Using Systemd
    # systemctl start candy@${foo}
    # systemctl enable candy@${foo}
